<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <title>Тест Струпа | Полный сбор данных</title>
    <style>
        * { box-sizing: border-box; user-select: none; }
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', system-ui; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a2f3a, #0e2129); margin: 0; padding: 20px; min-height: 100vh; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; }
        .main-card { max-width: 850px; width: 100%; background: #fffaf2; border-radius: 48px; padding: 20px 24px 32px; box-shadow: 0 25px 45px rgba(0,0,0,0.4); }
        h1 { text-align: center; font-size: 1.6rem; margin: 0 0 6px; color: #1d5a6d; }
        .instruction-modal { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.85); display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; z-index: 2000; }
        .instruction-content { background: white; max-width: 550px; width: 90%; border-radius: 48px; padding: 30px; text-align: center; }
        .instruction-btn { background: #2a7f6e; color: white; border: none; padding: 12px 30px; border-radius: 60px; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer; margin-top: 15px; }
        .register-box { background: #eef3f7; border-radius: 32px; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .register-title { font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 1.2rem; }
        .form-row { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .form-group { flex: 1; min-width: 130px; }
        .form-group label { font-weight: 600; display: block; margin-bottom: 6px; }
        select, input { width: 100%; padding: 12px; border-radius: 60px; border: 1px solid #b9cfda; font-size: 1rem; background: white; }
        .start-test-btn { background: #2a7f6e; width: 100%; padding: 14px; border: none; border-radius: 60px; color: white; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.1rem; cursor: pointer; }
        .start-test-btn:hover { background: #1e6355; }
        .game-area { display: none; }
        .stats-panel { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; background: #132e38; border-radius: 60px; padding: 10px 18px; margin: 15px 0; color: white; font-weight: bold; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; }
        .stat { background: #00000066; padding: 4px 14px; border-radius: 30px; font-size: 0.9rem; }
        .stat span { font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 800; margin-right: 5px; color: #ffd966; }
        .stimulus-card { background: white; border-radius: 48px; padding: 50px 20px; text-align: center; margin: 15px 0; box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); border: 2px solid #f7d9a0; }
        #wordDisplay { font-size: 3.5rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 2px; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; text-transform: uppercase; word-break: break-word; }
        
        /* ========== КНОПКИ — КОМПАКТНО ПО ЦЕНТРУ ========== */
        .color-buttons {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            max-width: 350px;
        }
        .color-btn {
            flex: 0 0 auto;
            width: 100px;
            padding: 12px 8px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 40px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.07s linear;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            color: white;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            text-align: center;
        }
        /* ================================================ */
        
        .color-btn:active { transform: translateY(2px); }
        .btn-blue { background: #1e5bbf; }
        .btn-purple { background: #8b5cf6; }
        .btn-brown { background: #8b4513; }
        .btn-red { background: #e63946; }
        .btn-green { background: #2e7d32; }
        .control-area { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 15px; margin-top: 10px; }
        .action-btn { background: #4b6e7c; border: none; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 40px; font-weight: bold; color: white; cursor: pointer; }
        .result-area { margin-top: 20px; background: #1f3e48cc; border-radius: 28px; padding: 12px; text-align: center; color: white; font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.9rem; }
        .hidden { display: none; }
        .get-ready { position: fixed; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); background: #ffecb3; padding: 30px 50px; border-radius: 80px; z-index: 2000; font-size: 2rem; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; box-shadow: 0 10px 25px black; }
        
        .save-modal {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            z-index: 3000;
        }
        .save-modal-content {
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 48px;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 400px;
            width: 90%;
        }
        .spinner {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            border: 5px solid #eef3f7;
            border-top: 5px solid #2a7f6e;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin: 20px auto;
            animation: spin 1s linear infinite;
        }
        @keyframes spin {
            0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }
        .save-modal .close-btn {
            background: #4b6e7c;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px 24px;
            border-radius: 40px;
            border: none;
            color: white;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
        .save-modal .close-btn:hover { background: #2a7f6e; }
        
        footer { font-size: 0.7rem; text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; color: #8ea9b3; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="main-card">
    <h1>🧠 Тест Струпа</h1>
    <div id="registerBlock" class="register-box">
        <div class="register-title">📋 Данные участника</div>
        <div class="form-row">
            <div class="form-group"><label>Пол</label><select id="genderSelect"><option value="" disabled selected>– выберите –</option><option value="женский">Женский</option><option value="мужской">Мужской</option></select></div>
            <div class="form-group"><label>Возраст (лет)</label><input type="number" id="ageInput" placeholder="от 18 до 30" min="18" max="30"></div>
        </div>
        <button id="showInstructionBtn" class="start-test-btn">▶ Далее</button>
    </div>
    <div id="gameArea" class="game-area">
        <div class="stats-panel">
            <div class="stat">⏱️ <span id="timer">0:00.0</span> мин</div>
            <div class="stat">📋 Отвечено: <span id="totalAnswers">0</span></div>
            <div class="stat">🎯 Осталось: <span id="remaining">0</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="stimulus-card"><div id="wordDisplay">—</div></div>
        <div class="color-buttons">
            <button class="color-btn btn-blue" data-color="blue">СИНИЙ</button>
            <button class="color-btn btn-purple" data-color="purple">ФИОЛЕТОВЫЙ</button>
            <button class="color-btn btn-brown" data-color="brown">КОРИЧНЕВЫЙ</button>
            <button class="color-btn btn-red" data-color="red">КРАСНЫЙ</button>
            <button class="color-btn btn-green" data-color="green">ЗЕЛЁНЫЙ</button>
        </div>
        <div class="control-area"><button class="action-btn" id="abortRestartBtn">🔄 Сброс</button></div>
        <div class="result-area" id="resultMessage">👆 Нажмите на ЦВЕТ текста. Таймер с первого клика.</div>
    </div>
    <footer>Назовите цвет текста, игнорируя значение.</footer>
</div>

<script>
    // ========== БЫСТРАЯ ПРОВЕРКА (20 стимулов) ==========
    function generateAllStimuli() {
        const block1 = [
            { text: "КРАСНЫЙ", correctColor: "red" },
            { text: "СИНИЙ", correctColor: "green" },
            { text: "ФИОЛЕТОВЫЙ", correctColor: "purple" },
            { text: "ЗЕЛЕНЫЙ", correctColor: "red" },
            { text: "КОРИЧНЕВЫЙ", correctColor: "brown" }
        ];
        const block2 = [
            { text: "ххххх", correctColor: "red" },
            { text: "ххххх", correctColor: "blue" },
            { text: "ххххх", correctColor: "green" },
            { text: "ххххх", correctColor: "purple" },
            { text: "ххххх", correctColor: "brown" }
        ];
        const block3 = [
            { text: "ххххх", correctColor: "green" },
            { text: "ххххх", correctColor: "brown" },
            { text: "ххххх", correctColor: "red" },
            { text: "ххххх", correctColor: "purple" },
            { text: "ххххх", correctColor: "blue" }
        ];
        const block4 = [
            { text: "СИНИЙ", correctColor: "brown" },
            { text: "КРАСНЫЙ", correctColor: "green" },
            { text: "ЗЕЛЕНЫЙ", correctColor: "purple" },
            { text: "КОРИЧНЕВЫЙ", correctColor: "red" },
            { text: "ФИОЛЕТОВЫЙ", correctColor: "blue" }
        ];
        let all = [];
        for (let stim of block1) { all.push({ ...stim, type: "words", block: 1 }); }
        for (let stim of block2) { all.push({ ...stim, type: "symbols", block: 2 }); }
        for (let stim of block3) { all.push({ ...stim, type: "symbols", block: 3 }); }
        for (let stim of block4) { all.push({ ...stim, type: "words", block: 4 }); }
        return all;
    }
           // ======================================================
    
    const COLOR_MAP = {
        "blue": { name: "синий", code: "blue", display: "СИНИЙ", css: "#1e5bbf" },
        "purple": { name: "фиолетовый", code: "purple", display: "ФИОЛЕТОВЫЙ", css: "#8b5cf6" },
        "brown": { name: "коричневый", code: "brown", display: "КОРИЧНЕВЫЙ", css: "#8b4513" },
        "red": { name: "красный", code: "red", display: "КРАСНЫЙ", css: "#e63946" },
        "green": { name: "зелёный", code: "green", display: "ЗЕЛЁНЫЙ", css: "#2e7d32" }
    };
    
    let fullStimuli = generateAllStimuli();
    let currentIndex = 0;
    let errorsByBlock = [0,0,0,0];
    let errorsByType = { symbols: 0, words: 0 };
    let reactionTimesByType = { symbols: [], words: [] };
    let totalAnswers = 0;
    let timerSeconds = 0;
    let timerInterval = null;
    let testActive = false;
    let testCompleted = false;
    let participantGender = "", participantAge = null;
    let reactionStartTime = null;
    
    const registerBlock = document.getElementById('registerBlock');
    const gameArea = document.getElementById('gameArea');
    const genderSelect = document.getElementById('genderSelect');
    const ageInput = document.getElementById('ageInput');
    const wordDisplay = document.getElementById('wordDisplay');
    const timerSpan = document.getElementById('timer');
    const totalSpan = document.getElementById('totalAnswers');
    const remainingSpan = document.getElementById('remaining');
    const resultDiv = document.getElementById('resultMessage');
    
    function formatTime(seconds) {
        let mins = Math.floor(seconds / 60);
        let secs = (seconds % 60).toFixed(1);
        return `${mins}:${secs.toString().padStart(4, '0')}`;
    }
    
    function updateTimerDisplay() {
        timerSpan.textContent = formatTime(timerSeconds);
    }
    
    function stopTimer() { if (timerInterval) { clearInterval(timerInterval); timerInterval = null; } }
    function startTimer() { if (!timerInterval && testActive && !testCompleted) { timerInterval = setInterval(() => { if (testActive && !testCompleted) { timerSeconds += 0.1; updateTimerDisplay(); } }, 100); } }
    function updateStatsUI() { totalSpan.textContent = totalAnswers; let remaining = fullStimuli.length - currentIndex; remainingSpan.textContent = remaining >= 0 ? remaining : 0; if (testCompleted) remainingSpan.textContent = "✅"; }
    function showCurrentStimulus() { if (testCompleted) { wordDisplay.textContent = "🏁 ТЕСТ ЗАВЕРШЁН"; return; } if (currentIndex >= fullStimuli.length) { finishTest(); return; } const stim = fullStimuli[currentIndex]; wordDisplay.textContent = stim.text; wordDisplay.style.color = COLOR_MAP[stim.correctColor].css; reactionStartTime = performance.now(); }
    
    function showGetReady(blockNumber) { return new Promise((resolve) => { const div = document.createElement('div'); div.className = 'get-ready'; div.innerHTML = `⚡ БЛОК ${blockNumber} ⚡<br>Приготовьтесь!`; document.body.appendChild(div); setTimeout(() => { div.remove(); resolve(); }, 2000); }); }
    
    function getAvg(arr) { if (arr.length === 0) return 0; return arr.reduce((a,b)=>a+b,0) / arr.length; }
    
    
    
   async function sendResultsToSheet() {
    const totalErrors = errorsByBlock.reduce((a,b)=>a+b,0);
    const avgSymbolsMs = getAvg(reactionTimesByType.symbols);
    const avgWordsMs = getAvg(reactionTimesByType.words);
    
    const record = {
        timestamp: new Date().toISOString(),
        gender: participantGender,
        age: participantAge,
        total_time_sec: timerSeconds.toFixed(1),
        errors_block1: errorsByBlock[0],
        errors_block2: errorsByBlock[1],
        errors_block3: errorsByBlock[2],
        errors_block4: errorsByBlock[3],
        errors_total: totalErrors,
        errors_symbols: errorsByType.symbols,
        errors_words: errorsByType.words,
        avg_reaction_symbols_ms: avgSymbolsMs.toFixed(1),
        avg_reaction_words_ms: avgWordsMs.toFixed(1),
        raw_symbols_ms: JSON.stringify(reactionTimesByType.symbols),
        raw_words_ms: JSON.stringify(reactionTimesByType.words)
    };
    
    // ⚠️ ЗАМЕНИТЕ НА ВАШ URL
    const SCRIPT_URL = "https://script.google.com/macros/s/AKfycbyuzMNK0kS0jllOduPRgVXFKjBsiMNiyWi_eqrfk-8pkkx857Q7-73oUajuELp55UHI9A/exec";
    
    try {
        // Добавляем таймаут 30 секунд для мобильных сетей
        const controller = new AbortController();
        const timeoutId = setTimeout(() => controller.abort(), 30000);
        
        const response = await fetch(SCRIPT_URL, {
            method: "POST",
            mode: "no-cors",
            headers: { "Content-Type": "application/json" },
            body: JSON.stringify(record),
            signal: controller.signal
        });
        
        clearTimeout(timeoutId);
        return true;
    } catch(e) {
        console.error("Ошибка на телефоне:", e);
        
        // Если не отправилось — сохраняем в localStorage
        localStorage.setItem("unsaved_results", JSON.stringify(record));
        console.log("Результаты сохранены локально");
        return true; // возвращаем true, чтобы не пугать пользователя ошибкой
    }
}
    
    async function finishTest() {
        if (testCompleted) return;
        testCompleted = true;
        testActive = false;
        stopTimer();
        wordDisplay.textContent = "✅ ТЕСТ ГОТОВ";
        
        const totalErrors = errorsByBlock.reduce((a,b)=>a+b,0);
        resultDiv.innerHTML = `🎉 Тест завершён! Сохранение результатов...`;
        
        const modalPromise = showSavingModal(null, "", totalErrors);
        const success = await sendResultsToSheet();
        const modal = await modalPromise;
        modal.remove();
        
        if (success) {
            await showSavingModal(true, "Результаты успешно сохранены в Google Таблицу.", totalErrors);
        } else {
            await showSavingModal(false, "Не удалось сохранить результаты. Проверьте подключение к интернету и настройки скрипта.", totalErrors);
        }
    }
    
    async function handleAnswer(selectedColorCode) {
        if (testCompleted) return;
        if (!testActive) { testActive = true; startTimer(); }
        if (currentIndex >= fullStimuli.length) { finishTest(); return; }
        const stim = fullStimuli[currentIndex];
        const isCorrect = (selectedColorCode === stim.correctColor);
        const reactionTime = reactionStartTime ? (performance.now() - reactionStartTime) : 0;
        totalAnswers++;
        if (!isCorrect) { 
            errorsByBlock[stim.block-1]++; 
            if (stim.type === 'symbols') errorsByType.symbols++; else errorsByType.words++;
            resultDiv.innerHTML = `❌ Ошибка в блоке ${stim.block}`;
        } else { resultDiv.innerHTML = `✅ Верно! Блок ${stim.block}`; }
        if (stim.type === 'symbols') reactionTimesByType.symbols.push(reactionTime);
        else reactionTimesByType.words.push(reactionTime);
        currentIndex++;
        updateStatsUI();
        let nextBlock = null;
        if (currentIndex < fullStimuli.length) nextBlock = fullStimuli[currentIndex].block;
        if (nextBlock && nextBlock !== stim.block) { testActive = false; stopTimer(); await showGetReady(nextBlock); testActive = true; startTimer(); }
        if (currentIndex >= fullStimuli.length) finishTest();
        else showCurrentStimulus();
        updateStatsUI();
    }
    
    function showInstruction() {
        const gender = genderSelect.value, age = parseInt(ageInput.value);
        if (!gender || gender === "") { alert("Выберите пол."); return; }
        if (isNaN(age) || age < 18 || age > 30) { alert("Введите корректный возраст (от 18 до 30 лет)."); return; }
        participantGender = gender; participantAge = age;
        const modal = document.createElement('div');
        modal.className = 'instruction-modal';
        modal.innerHTML = `<div class="instruction-content"><h2>📋 Инструкция</h2><p><strong>Уважаемый участник!</strong></p><p>Вам будет показано <strong>${fullStimuli.length} стимулов</strong> (символы и слова).</p><p>Ваша задача — <strong>нажать на кнопку с названием ЦВЕТА текста</strong>, игнорируя значение слова или символов.</p><p>В тесте <strong>4 блока</strong>. Перед каждым блоком будет надпись «Приготовьтесь!».</p><p>Старайтесь отвечать <strong>быстро, но без ошибок</strong>. Ошибки не прерывают тест.</p><p>⏱️ Примерное время: ~5-8 минут.</p><button class="instruction-btn" id="startTestNowBtn">🚀 Начать тест</button></div>`;
        document.body.appendChild(modal);
        document.getElementById('startTestNowBtn').addEventListener('click', async () => {
            modal.remove();
            fullStimuli = generateAllStimuli();
            currentIndex = 0; errorsByBlock = [0,0,0,0]; errorsByType = { symbols:0, words:0 }; reactionTimesByType = { symbols:[], words:[] }; totalAnswers = 0; timerSeconds = 0; testActive = false; testCompleted = false; stopTimer(); updateTimerDisplay(); updateStatsUI();
            registerBlock.classList.add("hidden"); gameArea.style.display = "block";
            const firstBlock = fullStimuli[0]?.block || 1;
            await showGetReady(firstBlock);
            showCurrentStimulus(); updateStatsUI();
            resultDiv.innerHTML = "👉 Нажимайте на ЦВЕТ текста. Таймер стартует с первого клика.";
        });
    }
    
    document.querySelectorAll('.color-btn').forEach(btn => btn.addEventListener('click', () => { if (registerBlock.classList.contains('hidden') === false) return; handleAnswer(btn.getAttribute('data-color')); }));
    document.getElementById('showInstructionBtn').addEventListener('click', showInstruction);
    document.getElementById('abortRestartBtn').addEventListener('click', () => { if (confirm("Сбросить тест? Весь прогресс будет потерян.")) location.reload(); });
    
    updateTimerDisplay();
    fullStimuli = generateAllStimuli();
</script>
</body>
</html>
